MITCH MCCONNELL DIDN‚ÄôT ‚ÄòSILENCE‚Äô ELIZABETH 'LIE-AWATHA' WARREN. HE TOOK HER TO SENATE SCHOOL
By: Brian Darling | February 08, 2017
J. Scott Applewhite | AP Images
